  <brief_title>Variation of Cerebral Blood Flow in Anterior Cerebral and Basilar Artery in Neonates and Infants in Genreal Anesthesia With Caudal Block</brief_title>
  <official_title>Variation of Cerebral Blood Flow in Anterior Cerebral and Basilar Artery in Neonates and Infants - a Prospective Study During Planed Surgery of the Infra Umbilical Region in Combined Anaesthesia</official_title>
