  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      With this study we want to see how the blood flow in the anterior cerebral artery (ACA) and
      the basilar artery (BA) after the caudal block changes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Enrolling by invitation</overall_status>
  <start_date>January 2016</start_date>
